{"tid":55034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸名醫教學生　如何宰病人賺錢","createTime":"2016-12-26T05:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T07:57:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c20f53fd20c0d75e70789223e4de318d2ca515a1","tid":55034,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"這就是鬼國，一切只向錢看！<br />\n<br />\n【大陸名醫教學生　如何宰病人賺錢】<br />\n<br />\n「人家都收紅包，你憑甚麼不收！患者得表示感謝！」<br />\n「所以不知道大家聽完這個經濟利益以後，你學習有動力嗎？反正我每天上班就跟打雞血一樣，幹活非常有勁！」<br />\n<br />\n他是北大航天中心醫院泌尿外科醫生李睿，擅長治療前列腺增生，不育等男科疾病，亦是私人教育機構西醫研究生考試教學名師。<br />\n他上堂時，說最好賺的，是做闌尾炎和結石手術。<br />\n<br />\n「闌尾炎五分鐘一台，十分鐘一台，你連續排好隊一垛，止血紗布、上血粉，那就好了。」<br />\n「一個病人，你可別笑，一個結石，像我們泌尿外科，一個結石，一個體外碎石，一個病人 1,200 元，如果一個晚上遇上十個結石，一萬二！那叫『瘋狂的石頭』，比鑽石都值錢！」<br />\n<br />\n這樣教學生，難怪引來罵聲一片，批評他是「庸醫」、「誤人子弟」，但有關教育機構指片段並非他們的網上課程內容，只屬個人言論，而醫院方面就指，這個醫生已經離職五個月。<br />\n但網上不少評論認為，其實他也只是道出殘酷的事實真相。<br />\n<br />\n「我這個月在科室的分紅，是一塑料袋，聽懂了嗎！沒辦法，醫生就是這種好處嘛！．．．我肯定付出就得有回報啊！沒回報，我白為共產黨奉獻，我也不幹啊！」"},{"pid":"87673aebe86b4d2c70a66f15247952f84633d117","tid":55034,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb45b6724a0e5b28d3ba77c582e10db4069c64f","tid":55034,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ada56adb242d3c051a2a070bacef22096218c1f","tid":55034,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"佢講出真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54606098e6f8fa8297f1a8cf1d6a6b7551fa9303","tid":55034,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢講出真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仁醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0428a922f54e64d5629a6c1be9cf725a243368fe","tid":55034,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b01f66bd432ab703fe440b6ba66f4fcbde77b02","tid":55034,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀醫科真係開善堂懸壺濟世咩，都係睇錢途姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係唔撚信讀medicine個d真係有人真心想救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebdee625f8290a700b9248483f261131eb4661e","tid":55034,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:27:18.000Z","msg":"有錢人讀醫可能為夢想既<br />\n中產同窮人讀醫唔多唔少都係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad5a5835806af545a0059e5e3b79a47de4bab32","tid":55034,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀醫科真係開善堂懸壺濟世咩，都係睇錢途姐</blockquote><br />\n所以贈醫施藥一直係崇高既理想"},{"pid":"43e4e710832ed3e9d7b10dbf3ee35faeaac792ba","tid":55034,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢人讀醫可能為夢想既<br />\n中產同窮人讀醫唔多唔少都係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cd31b079d197081fe8773aa5a99bf7ff9b7bed53","tid":55034,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"所以你話港英遺產幾咁可貴"},{"pid":"f7469eb32efbd105e5914ab6a66ab7018ad4a852","tid":55034,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以你話港英遺產幾咁可貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係香港醫生人工高未使去到呢步<br />\n2047之後咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3776e12c3d9acdad2321c1dfc16d936403826c","tid":55034,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"邊到都係嫁啦，好出奇呀"},{"pid":"891820dab1a8975e1809477e906ca350c8e6e7f4